{"tid":2010932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日一有警暴虐待親子既文宣，就有人跳出黎話片/相中人係「藍絲」","createTime":"2020-05-10T16:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T02:01:04.000Z","uid":90601,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4af6877315bc14cf9e268f57ce17b11525946918","tid":2010932,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T16:47:52.000Z","msg":"有線個阿媽同兩個女出黎慶祝母親節食宵夜，兩個女比人拉左<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/awAeEdU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/awAeEdU</a><br />\n<br />\n有線個阿媽同兩個女出黎慶祝母親節食宵夜，兩個女比人拉左<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/awAeEdU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/awAeEdU</a><br />\n<br />\n今日母親節，但pk鄧旗下既23k冰團又再次做左英明既行動<br />\n成功攬炒左成個母親足足一日<br />\n為各位提供大家和理非文宣素材<br />\n<br />\n有趣既係<br />\n每當有親子/細佬被防暴 子彈 胡椒球彈所影響<br />\n就會人跳出黎宣稱當事人 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有可能係藍絲</span></span><br />\n例：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GSUH7Qd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGSUH7Qd.png&h=cbe30dcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7TR7zve.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7TR7zve.png&h=04c39488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係依度想提出兩件事<br />\n<strong>一、就算當事人係藍屍，但係佢無否認受警暴影響，咁視覺及內容上佢已經係受害人，已足以構成文宣<br />\n二、文宣應追求結果，唔需要有潔癖。我地唔係製造fake news：bb仔因為槍聲而喊；兩個細路女落街同老母食消夜被拉，已經係事實，已經有文宣效果</strong><br />\n<br />\n至於點解咁多人衝出黎洗淡「母親節親子受害文宣」既效果<br />\n相信唔洗多講<br />\ntwitter見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0861897126337132fefd7a17205b7299b0b378f","tid":2010932,"uid":90601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T16:49:21.000Z","msg":"其中一條link貼錯左 補返<br />\n<br />\n母親節 黑警9射胡椒球彈 BB中椒喊得好淒涼<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ftocMS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ftocMS</a>"},{"pid":"85a4bddd524552bb732f0f79fd9ec01bebd7afba","tid":2010932,"uid":49018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T16:50:19.000Z","msg":"充分利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa04a11d076b50a381ceda81cd99d62e5f59d605","tid":2010932,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T16:51:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aaf65427a5bd53e5468ce2d7ec1d8c79314f842f","tid":2010932,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T16:52:58.000Z","msg":"理撚得佢咩人   有故做尻d狗咪得   係藍屍仲好tim"},{"pid":"acdbe945960c7a458163e650c8305f3df26034ab","tid":2010932,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T16:53:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4dec8dccb50b2c0fc086290fe54c25d6bea9bc82","tid":2010932,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad64c262dacbcd8cbd3d90dde49c83bdd32cf33","tid":2010932,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T16:55:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f709911d47732027aa7aadbf4ebdad07133991e2","tid":2010932,"uid":82628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T16:57:05.000Z","msg":"放上save hk 鬥藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64eedf87794a56aaee45195acb73a053e11cb01b","tid":2010932,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T16:57:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ArmChannelTV/photos/a.331706413625439/2747991191996937/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FArmChannelTV%2Fphotos%2Fa.331706413625439%2F2747991191996937%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQrTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=bd7511bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ht